body: "Files .agents/pm/tasks/pm-mb4n.toon and .agents/pm/tasks/pm-cakn.toon contain references to steve@192.168.1.183 in comment/evidence text and linked test commands. While not a credential leak (private IP, no passwords), this is unnecessary information exposure. These references were left from prior audit runs. The linked test in pm-cakn has an SSH command targeting the private host. Remediation: redact the private IP from committed pm items."
